OL,3,CMan shot in the legs in Croxteth
OL,5,FAn investigation is underway following
OL,6,Freports a man was shot in the legs in
OL,7,FCroxteth.
OL,9,FOfficers were contacted at just after
OL,10,F10.10pm last night, Friday 28
OL,11,FFebruary, following reports the man,
OL,12,Fwho is in his 40s, had been shot on
OL,13,FAltcross Road.
OL,15,FThe man was taken to hospital for
OL,16,Ftreatment for his injuries which are
OL,17,Fnot believed to be life threatening.
OL,19,FAn investigation is underway and
OL,20,Fforensic, CCTV and witness enquiries
OL,21,Fare ongoing in the local area.
