OL,5,FDetective Inspector Joanne Jacob said:
OL,6,F"The investigation is in the very
OL,7,Fearly stages as we seek to establish
OL,8,Fwhat has taken place.
OL,10,F"We are keen to speak to anyone who
OL,11,Fwas in the area of Altcross Road at
OL,12,Faround 10pm last night who saw or
OL,13,Fheard anything suspicious or believes
OL,14,Fthey captured something significant on
OL,15,Ftheir dashcam, CCTV or doorbell camera.
OL,17,F"We know that guns cause misery on our
OL,18,Fstreets and we would ask for the
OL,19,Fpublic's help in coming forward with
OL,20,Fany information they have so we can
OL,21,Ffind the person or people responsible.
