OL,5,F"Merseyside Police is committed to
OL,6,Fremoving firearms from our streets and
OL,7,Fbringing those who carry or use them
OL,8,Fto justice and we would ask our
OL,9,Fcommunities to help us by coming
OL,10,Fforward and telling us what they know."
